PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781532675
OL,3,C'It's just unbelievable': Bank of Dave
OL,4,Cstar honoured with OBE
OL,6,FHe grew up in a poor family in Nelson,
OL,7,FLancashire, but made his fortune
OL,8,Fsupplying minibuses before opening an
OL,9,Findependent lending company to support
OL,10,Fpeople following the 2008 financial
OL,11,Fcrash.
OL,13,FHe received his OBE for services to
OL,14,Ffinance, business, and charity.
OL,16,FThe 55-year-old businessman-turned-
OL,17,Fphilanthropist said: "It's just
OL,18,Fwonderful that His Majesty the King
OL,19,Fhas spent some time looking at what
OL,20,Fwe've been doing and seen fit to award
OL,21,Fus an OBE.
OL,26,@yD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
