OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781532675
OL,3,C'It's just unbelievable': Bank of Dave
OL,4,Cstar honoured with OBE
OL,6,F"It's just unbelievable. And from a
OL,7,Flad from Burnley, who set off with
OL,8,Fabsolutely no qualifications
OL,9,Fwhatsoever ` I left school at 16,
OL,10,Fabsolutely useless."
OL,12,FDave said when he left school he had
OL,13,Fno choice but to go straight into
OL,14,Fworking on building sites for just
OL,15,Funder #30 a week.
OL,17,FThe entrepreneur juggled three jobs,
OL,18,Fselling clothes at Smithfield Market
OL,19,Fin Manchester in the morning, working
OL,20,Fon building sites in the day, and
OL,21,FDJing at nightclubs in the evenings.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]
