OL,3,C'It's just unbelievable': Bank of Dave
OL,4,Cstar honoured with OBE
OL,6,FBefore founding Burnley Saving and
OL,7,FLoans in 2011, Dave said he dreamed of
OL,8,Fworking on cars but could not even
OL,9,Fafford a gallon of petrol, instead he
OL,10,Fwent around dozens of garages asking
OL,11,Fif there was an old part-exchange car
OL,12,Fhe could take away, do up and sell to
OL,13,Fkeep a portion of the profits.
OL,15,FHe said: "I did it again and again,
OL,16,Fand that just shows sometimes you've
OL,17,Fgot to think outside the box, because
OL,18,Fyou can start with absolutely nothing,
OL,19,Fand it's not where you start that
OL,20,Fmatters, it's where you finish that
OL,21,Fcounts.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
