PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781532675
OL,3,C'It's just unbelievable': Bank of Dave
OL,4,Cstar honoured with OBE
OL,6,F"This award from the King just shows
OL,7,Fthat if you put your mind to it, you
OL,8,Fcan achieve anything, and you can come
OL,9,Ffrom the north, you really can come
OL,10,Ffrom the north of England and still
OL,11,Fhave opportunities like lots of people
OL,12,Fdo in the south."
OL,14,FThe story of its success and Dave's
OL,15,Finvestigations into loan sharks were
OL,16,Fadapted for 2023's Bank of Dave,
OL,17,Fstarring Rory Kinnear, and its sequel
OL,18,FBank of Dave 2: The Loan Ranger,
OL,19,Freleased in 2025.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@QO]
