OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781532675
OL,3,C'It's just unbelievable': Bank of Dave
OL,4,Cstar honoured with OBE
OL,6,FDave said: "If Dave from Burnley with
OL,7,Fabsolutely nothing can make it happen,
OL,8,Fthen you can too,"
OL,10,F"So it's really important that we get
OL,11,Fthe message out that if you put your
OL,12,Fmind to it, self-belief,
OL,13,Fdetermination."
OL,15,FThe profits from Burnley Savings and
OL,16,FLoans, which has the slogan "Bank on
OL,17,FDave", go to good causes, often in
OL,18,FLancashire.
OL,26,@nD@LOUpD@RO]rD@AOUuD@OO]xD@]OUyD@EO]
