OL,3,C'It's just unbelievable': Bank of Dave
OL,4,Cstar honoured with OBE
OL,6,FHe said he credits his "right-hand
OL,7,Fman" David Henshaw, his wife Nicky and
OL,8,Fthe team behind Bank of Dave for his
OL,9,Fcontinued success as he takes on new
OL,10,Fprojects, including becoming the
OL,11,Fambassador for 6,000 community banks
OL,12,Fin the US.
OL,14,FAs for what is next for him, Dave said
OL,15,Fhe would like to continue his
OL,16,Fcampaigning and sharing money advice.
OL,18,FHe has also said he was invited to
OL,19,Ftake part in Strictly Come Dancing -
OL,20,Fbut admitted he cannot dance.
OL,26,@nD@XOUoD@DO]
